name: Under pressure by Mael Barbosa
description:
"This work brings a reflection of the present day, to which we live in an agitated world, where people get sick psychologically, and consequently physical exhaustion.
They kill to win, and then spend what they've earned to relieve stress to regain their mental and physical health."

"Remember, in your profession, you are not paid to stress, you are paid to work"
